 Symposium on Conceptual Modeling Education

Please consider submitting a paper to the 6th Symposium on Conceptual
Modeling Education (SCME 2018), which will be held
in conjunction with the 37th International Conference on Conceptual
Modeling (ER 2018),
in Xi'an, one of the historical capitals of China, from the 22d to the
